{"tid":1739522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[空氣污染指標] HKU公共衞生學院 達理指數 - 11月空氣污染日數達100%","createTime":"2019-11-19T15:19:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T15:21:22.000Z","uid":335235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dc2a4b0e9805c0cc79580ce6ffd1d94a187c472e","tid":1739522,"uid":335235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:19:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hedleyindex.hku.hk/zh/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhedleyindex.hku.hk%2Fzh%2F&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqCwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=09685c94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hedleyindex.hku.hk/zh/</a><br />\n<strong>香港大學公共衞生學院 達理指數<br />\nHedley Environmental Index, School of Public Health, HKU</strong><br />\n<br />\n清新日是指任何一天當中，十三個市區天台監測站所測量的五個標準污染物的濃度，都符合世界衞生組織 (WHO) 短期空氣質素指引。我們以綠色代表<span style=\"color: green;\">清新日</span>，灰色代表<span style=\"color: red;\">污染日</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>污染日/總日數</strong></span></ins><br />\n6月: 6/30 (20%)<br />\n7月: 4/31 (13%)<br />\n8月: 7/31 (23%)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">9月: 15/30 (50%)</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">10月: 27/31 (87%)</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">11月(截至18/11): 18/18 (100%)</span></strong>"},{"pid":"f1253924d68f0268348a7661087dedef7f2d703b","tid":1739522,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:21:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>入嚟睇致勝關鍵！！！！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n[拒絕分化！]古人一早教我地點贏<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1739422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1739422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n[正能量撚]出去之前，希望你可以睇下呢個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>全個連登都係負能量，我要你地有正能量啊</strong></span></span>